media:group.media:description:
SUBSCRIBE to Truly: http://bit.ly/Oc61Hj

LINSEY Donovan has some exciting news. The 23-year-old has been searching for her dream home for a couple of years now and today, she’s showing her mum, Mary, around a property that might just be the one. Will this $3 million, 4-bed, 7-bathroom house become home to Linsey and all her animals? Linsey has another surprise in store for her mum, who is incredibly proud of her daughter. Mary told Truly: “I think people underestimate my daughter because she’s so young - they have no idea how mature and smart she is. My daughter’s very persistent and because of that, she will get what she wants.” Linsey has a drive for success and is determined to reach her goals. She told Truly: “There’s people that work their whole lives and never get to live their dream out so I feel really lucky that I made my dreams actually come true and I get to share it with my family.”
